{"tid":1837671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸啲外賣仔會唔會成為超級傳播者？","createTime":"2020-01-23T17:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T10:02:23.000Z","uid":71237,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4fedd5c059d6a9b5f7fcbd6d99aa590977d298d6","tid":1837671,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"見到有人比較今次武漢肺炎同埋2003年SARS。好多人都指出今次有高鐵，所以傳播得特別勁。<br />\n其實仲有一個無咩人提及嘅因素，就係外賣apps。<br />\n<br />\n2003年果陣雖然都有外賣，不過一個外賣仔通常只為一間餐廳服務。<br />\n而家大陸啲外賣apps (e.g. 美團外賣)好盛行，一個外賣仔幾乎全個走遍整個社區，一旦感染容易成為超級傳播者。<br />\n有啲外賣仔可能見張單送得遠，就吐啲口水落個客啲食物度，加速病毒傳播。"},{"pid":"7aa5073ae73754cee1e4e8f9db9128f5928bfc22","tid":1837671,"uid":104138,"like":68,"dislike":2,"score":66,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:23:02.000Z","msg":"有啲外賣仔可能見張單送得遠，就吐啲口水落個客啲食物度，加速病毒傳播。<br />\n<br />\n本來睇到好認真，睇到呢到笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931dce90f68a1b7cc5b04f1adcbdcba410e9d3f8","tid":1837671,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"推上去重要野！<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a3497b8e15d6776ec8263e6a02ccf0c2d9f796af","tid":1837671,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7aa5073ae73754cee1e4e8f9db9128f5928bfc22","tid":1837671,"uid":104138,"like":68,"dislike":2,"score":66,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:23:02.000Z","msg":"有啲外賣仔可能見張單送得遠，就吐啲口水落個客啲食物度，加速病毒傳播。<br />\n<br />\n本來睇到好認真，睇到呢到笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"外賣仔真係做得出 <img src=\"/assets/